dialogue.introduction: First ship of the Yuugumo-class, Yuugumo, has arrived. Admiral, it's okay to spoil me a bit.
dialogue.library_intro: First ship of the final mass-production destroyers. Laid down in Maizuru. My first battle was the ignominious defeat at Midway. It's okay, I don't mind. In the Tokyo Express to that island, Operation Ke, the Battle of the Santa Cruz Islands and the evacuation of Kiska, I fought bravely, no? *sigh*
dialogue.secretary1: Admiral, let's do our best together.
dialogue.secretary3: Yes yes what is it~? Admiral, Makigumo, you're so fond of skinship, no?
dialogue.secretaryidle: Aren't you tired Admiral? Yuugumo is quite worried you know...
dialogue.secretarymarried: Admiral~ is it not a good time to take a quick break?
dialogue.wedding: Ah, Admiral~, your hat is askance again. You're the commander of such a big fleet, please do look the part. Just how much do I have to look after you… eh? It's fine to keep on doing it? Well, that’s・just・lovely♡
dialogue.show_players_score: A report from headquarters. Please examine it.
dialogue.joining_a_fleet: Destroyer Yuugumo, going with full force!
dialogue.equipment2: Many thanks, I will use it well.
dialogue.equipment3: Yuugumo is being remodeled. No peeping.
dialogue.expedition_selection: Yuugumo is being remodeled. No peeping.
dialogue.resource_collection: Yuugumo is being remodeled. No peeping.
dialogue.instant_repair: Yuugumo is being remodeled. No peeping.
dialogue.development: Yuugumo is being remodeled. No peeping.
dialogue.docking_moderate_damage: Sorry, I might have to be in the bath for a while. I've been a bit exhausted lately.
dialogue.ship_construction: A new ship has been launched, no?
dialogue.return_from_sortie: The fleet has returned from the operation.
dialogue.night_battle: Mi~ss Makigumo, If you are talking about a night battle, this is how you do it!
dialogue.night_attack: I say this gonna be quite interesting.
dialogue.artillery_spotting: I say this gonna be quite interesting.
dialogue.night_special_attack_modifier_cutin_at_n: I say this gonna be quite interesting.
dialogue.support_expedition_team_arrival: I say this gonna be quite interesting.
dialogue.mvp: Admiral, choosing me was a good idea, yes?
dialogue.minor_damaged1: Ah... Armour, I don't really have any, yes?
dialogue.minor_damaged2: Kya! This level... I can still go on!
dialogue.moderately_damaged: Kyaaaa! Now you've really done it.... I-I'll return this twice over!
dialogue.sunk: Oh... I'm sinking too, no? Admiral... thanks for everything... up to now... See you... later...

hourly.0100: It's 1 A.M... Zzz... Oh, please excuse me.
hourly.0200: It is now 2 A.M. You have to go to sleep, yes?
hourly.0300: It's 3 A.M. I just can't leave the Admiral by himself...
hourly.0400: 4 A.M. A visitor at this time?
hourly.0500: 5 A.M. I wondered who it was, Mi~ss Makigumo. I wasn't there so you came to look for me, yes?
hourly.0600: 6 A.M. Miss Makigumo.... t-this... I was with the Admiral all night... planning battle strategy...
hourly.0700: 7 A.M. Well then Admiral, I'll be heading back with Miss Makigumo to our room.
hourly.0800: 8 A.M.... Once again, it's Yuugumo. Explaining to Miss Makigumo and getting her to understand was difficult.
hourly.0900: 9 A.M. Admiral, shall we check the rankings? Let us put in a fun comment!
hourly.1000: 10 A.M. The first fleet's name, shall we change it?
hourly.1100: 11 A.M. I thought it was an interesting name, but I wonder why the admins checked it? What a bother.
hourly.1200: 12 midday. Treating Yuugumo is okay, no?
hourly.1300: 1 P.M. hmm~ After eating, I get tired, no? Wait, Yuugumo didn't sleep yesterday!
hourly.1400: It's 2 P.M. Are you really not tired? I have heard that a midday nap is good for mental activity, no?
hourly.1500: 3 P.M. Admiral, the new rankings have been released, no? Let us have a look.
hourly.1600: 4 P.M, the sun has set a bit, no?
hourly.1700: 5 P.M. I wonder who today's best shipdaughter is? Naturally, it's Yuugumo, yes?
hourly.1800: 6 P.M. Dinner with just the two of us, I'm looking forward to it.
hourly.1900: 7 P.M. Tonight's dinner will be made by Yuugumo!
hourly.2000: 8 P.M. Admiral, was it tasty? Was it?
hourly.2100: It's 9 P.M. Ah, Miss Makigumo is watching from the gap. Sorry Admiral, I'll be heading back now.
hourly.2200: 10 P.M. Would it not be amicable to have a bath soon?
hourly.2300: 11 P.M. hmm? Admiral, let us retire early today.
